1. Search for domain
This can only be done in our ready database

2. Search for keyword
This can also be done only in our ready database

3. Search ads from a channel
This can also be done only in our ready database

4. Follow a channel
Keep an eye on a channel's video and see who is targeting it

5. Follow a video
Keep an eye on a video and see who is targeting it

6. New ads
report the new ads collected (datewise?)

So basically... The ad collection works by 
1. Chrome plugin that is embedded on people's browsers
2. A limited set of crawlers that are following channels and videos

=====

You have to create a meanderer... A crawler that just keeps visiting random youtube videos.
How will you do that?